%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“我已将它置放在楼梯处，去那处拿取吧！”阿难尊者说。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“尊者！您以手碰触过的任何物品，我的主人是不会取回的。”于是，侍女空手而返。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">毘舍佉问︰“亲爱的女孩！情况如何？”那侍女如实地向毘舍佉报告。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“亲爱的女孩！我不会使用任何尊者碰触过的物品，我将赠予尊者。然而，照顾这座宝冠徒使尊者增添困扰。我将把它卖了，再供养适合之物。你去将它取回吧！”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">毘舍佉并没有再度戴上它，她将宝冠送至金匠处估价。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">金匠们说︰“这宝冠价值九千万，手艺价值一百千。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">于是，毘舍佉将巨蔓宝冠放在一头大象身上，在城中展示并开放出售。然而，无人付得起这般价码，况且配得上此座宝冠的女人太难找了。事实上，世上仅有三位女人有能力拥有巨蔓宝冠︰佛陀的弟子毘舍佉、摩罗国般度罗</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Bandula）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">将军之妻末利迦</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Mallikā）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">及波罗奈国王之女。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 2em;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 2em;">在无法觅得买者的情况下，毘舍佉亲自将此宝冠买下， 将九千万又一百千放上运货马车，运载至寺院。&nbsp;</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">她礼敬佛陀后，说︰“世尊！阿难尊者曾保管我的宝冠，从他碰触宝冠的那一刻起，我不可能再戴上它。我几经努力欲将它卖了，想将卖后所得用在供养僧众适合的物品上。但是，我见无人有能力买下这座宝冠，于是自己将它买下，并将这些款项带来了。世尊！我应供养四资具的哪一项呢？”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“毘舍佉！在东门建造一座僧众的住处是适宜的。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“世尊！此最适宜不过了！”</span><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 2em;">毘舍佉以欢喜心，耗资九千万买下一块地，再以另外九千万开始建寺。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 0em;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(2, 30, 170);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">欢喜建鹿母讲堂</span></strong></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Adobe Song Std L&quot;;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">有一次，佛陀见跋提雅</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Bhaddiya）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">证悟的因缘已成熟，决定前往度化。佛陀在给孤独长者</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Anāthapiṇḍika）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">家应供后，前往北门。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">依照佛陀的惯例，若佛陀在毘舍佉家应供，则会往南门出城，住在祇树给孤独园</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Jetavana Anāthapiṇḍikassa Ārāma）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">。若佛陀在给孤独长者家应供，则会往东门，住在东园</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Pubbārāma）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">。当佛陀在清晨出北门，人们知道佛陀即将游方远处。因此，当毘舍佉得悉佛陀及僧众们往北门走时，她急忙赶到该处向佛陀礼敬，并说︰“世尊！您要游方远处吗？”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“是的，毘舍佉！”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“世尊！以那巨大的款项，我正为您盖一座寺院，能否等待寺院完成呢？”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“毘舍佉！这一趟旅程无法延后。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“好的，世尊如是说必然有其原因。倘若如此，世尊能否指定一些善于工程的僧众留下？”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“毘舍佉！你心中想让谁留下，可前去将其钵拿下。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">毘舍佉虽然喜爱阿难尊者，但是想着目犍连尊者具大神通，若有尊者的帮忙，寺院的工程必定能顺利进展。于是，她拿下了目犍连尊者的钵。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">目犍连尊者目视佛陀。</span><span style="text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;">佛陀说︰“目犍连！带着你训练的五百弟子折返回去。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">目犍连尊者遵照佛陀的指示。以尊者们的神通力，他们能到达远至五十至六十由旬处收集石头及木材，并在同一天将巨大的石头及木头运回。他们毫不费力地将材料运上车，而车轴并没有因此而断坏。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不久，一座拥有高平地基的双层建筑随即耸立而起，内有千间套房，上下层各有五百。为增添此寺的美观及实用性，毘舍佉增建五百小禅室、五百僧寮及五百阶梯，环绕于主建筑的周围。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">佛陀游方九个月后再度返回舍卫城。那时，在目犍连尊者的监督下，毘舍佉的建寺工程已经完成。她将犹如六十盛水器皿般宽大的鎏金宝顶，作为寺院的刹顶。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">得知佛陀在祇树给孤独园，她前往谒见佛陀，并诚意邀请佛陀及比丘僧团住在那已竣工的寺院，她将举办寺院捐赠典礼。此座寺院名为鹿母讲堂</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（Migāramātupāsāda）</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">她对佛陀作出邀请︰“世尊！请与比丘众们在鹿母讲堂安居四个月。”佛陀默然而许。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">自此，毘舍佉以丰足的四资具，供养佛陀及住在该寺的僧众。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">有一次，毘舍佉的一位朋友带着一片价值千金的布来见她，并说︰“我希望能更换建筑内覆盖地面之布，请以这片布取而代之。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“亲爱的朋友！若我告诉你，已无可放置之处，你或会想︰‘她不让出空间给我。’请你亲自巡视这双层建筑的地板及千间套房，并自己找地方放置。”</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">于是，她带着这块价值千金的布，仔细观察建筑的每一处，但找不到任何尚未置放地面布之处，而且每一片已置放在寺院的地面布，价值都比她手中这块布来得昂贵许多。她感到万分沮丧，心想︰“我无法参与建造此座寺院的功德。”她伫立在该处难过地哭泣。&nbsp;</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 2em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">阿难尊者见到她，问道︰“你为何哭泣？”她如实地将 情况告诉阿难尊者。&nbsp;</span></section><section style="margin-right: